<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="Spartas Agency: Creative digital agency specializing in modern websites and brand identities for ambitious businesses.">
    <meta name="keywords" content="digital agency, web design, branding, Spartas">
    <title>Spartas Agency - Home</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@700&family=Roboto:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            color: #000000;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        header {
            background-color: #000000;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
        }
        .logo {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2em;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #c0c0c0;
        }
        nav {
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        nav a {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        nav a:hover {
            color: #c0c0c0;
        }
        .hero {
            background-image: url('hero-bg.jpg'); /* Replace with your image */
            background-color: #000000; /* Fallback color to avoid white gap */
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            padding: 80px 20px; /* Reduced padding for less gap */
            text-align: center;
            color: #ffffff;
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in;
        }
        .hero h1 {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            font-size: 3em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        section {
            padding: 50px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        #services {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }
        .services-grid {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .service-item {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            flex: 1 1 300px;
            max-width: 300px;
        }
        footer {
            background-color: #000000;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; }
            to { opacity: 1; }
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 { font-size: 2em; }
            .services-grid { flex-direction: column; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="logo">Spartas</div>
        <nav>
            <a href="index.html">Home</a>
            <a href="contact.html">Contact</a>
        </nav>
    </header>
    
    <section class="hero">
        <h1>Welcome to Spartas Agency</h1>
        <p>Spartas Agency is a creative digital agency specializing in crafting modern, high-impact websites and brand identities for ambitious businesses. We combine innovation, design, and strategy to deliver digital experiences that capture attention and drive real results.</p>
    </section>
    
    <section id="services">
        <h2>Our Services</h2>
        <div class="services-grid">
            <div class="service-item">
                <h3>Web Design</h3>
                <p>Modern, responsive websites that engage users and drive conversions.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-item">
                <h3>Branding</h3>
                <p>Unique brand identities that stand out and build lasting connections.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-item">
                <h3>Digital Strategy</h3>
                <p>Data-driven strategies to maximize your online presence and results.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2023 Spartas Agency. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>Follow us: <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ahmed-reda-632134366" style="color: #c0c0c0;"><i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i></a></p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
